Subject: [Bioc-devel] AMI Policy Change
Message-ID: <BL1PR12MB5301393837A875D57D919D4BF9E42@BL1PR12MB5301.namprd12.prod.outlook.com>

In the past Bioconductor provided pre-configured AMI with certain Bioconductor releases, conferences, and workshops.  We are moving these legacy AMI snapshots to a cold storage class. They will be available by request only; The time necessary for retrieval may range from 12 to 72 hours. These AMIs contain obsolete versions of operating systems and thus have many security vulnerabilities. Not all past releases and conferences are available as we have transitioned to providing other platforms and infrastructure like docker images. If there are any concerns please let us know by May 15





